{"tid":1949874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父親因金錢問題被兒子擸刀斬傷 ！！","createTime":"2020-03-30T03:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T03:22:32.000Z","uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"30fab43452e384f4d74af74296cda0ebab50a489","tid":1949874,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOFVm0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOFVm0e.jpg&h=d72f8d60&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屯門發生逆子斬父案件。今日(30日)凌晨1時許，鍾氏兩父子(51歲及19歲)在大興邨興耀樓一單位內，因金錢問題爭執，期間兒子從廚房取出菜刀襲擊父親，導致父他頭、手及胸受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕至調查，並召救護車將受傷的父親送院治理，兒子涉嫌傷人被捕，屯門警區刑事調查隊跟進案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200330/mobile/bkn-20200330065000073-0330_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200330%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200330065000073-0330_00822_001.html&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=58eebfc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200330/mobile/bkn-20200330065000073-0330_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b337fc4e89f10b0531e37025f38a6c51c6d5cca7","tid":1949874,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"259917e9a6c856178ec1d457f64aa6f23f3a63a5","tid":1949874,"uid":320293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"仔打老豆 菩薩保佑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2796320a4425d6b202a156ac819ef84b6cca4a","tid":1949874,"uid":76854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"拎法包打咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7bccfcb86216bcd44af56a0cebd0bbfb26a0e9","tid":1949874,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"屌 無法式麵包嘅"},{"pid":"0a2b8a6f32bed21777afbd2